onumber\] \[=\dfrac{\sqrt{3} }{2} \dfrac{\sqrt{2} }{2} -\dfrac{1}{2} \dfrac{\sqrt{2} }{2}\quad \dfrac{\sqrt{6} -\sqrt{2} }{4}
